reviewText: Everyone should get this set and pay careful attention to what Pastor Prince is teaching. This is the most outstanding teaching on communion I have ever come accross.

I am most truly enjoying this Joseph Prince teaching Series because it awakening me with revelation know and wisdom of what Christ has done for me and how I am to partake of Him and experience His goodness provided to us when participating in the most Holy Communion.

There are not enough words to describe the depth, richness and character of the teachings of Joseph Prince.  He teaches through his relationship with Jesus.  His anointing is powerful and clear, and this message that Joseph brings to his brothers and sisters is a complete re-write of what we, devout Christians, have been taught about The LORD's Supper.  This particular teaching came as confirmation for me, after a death-dealing diagnosis of metastatic cancer.  I am cancer-free, healthy and well.  Praise the life-giving blood of Jesus, and bless those whom He has raised up to teach us!  This teaching is a MUST for all The Church.

This Cd set is a powerful teaching on The Holy Communion a must for anyone looking for more depth into God's awesome purpose in Communion. If you are dealing with sickness this is a must see teaching.... God has freedom through His communion!
A must have, thank you.  Fast del
This is an awesome and progressive revelation from the Holy Spirit that is deep and life-changing!  Worth EVERY penny and more!
Excellent condition.  Very helpful added information.  Would continue to purchase from this vendor.  Holy Communion and this resource has indeed been a blessing to me, my family and my friends.
As a Christian, this teaching is a mind opening to discern the true meaning of Holy Communion.  I wish I knew about the teaching when Joseph Prince fisrt taught in 2002.
Thank you so much for sending it so fast  if i could i would give you 10 stars .......

Joseph Prince once again gives us an excellent teaching on the Holy Communion. Never ever had communion been taught to me this way. Joseph Prince brings reality to what Holy Communion is all about. I would recommend this for your family and church to learn the reality of the Holy Communion. Prince brings light to the way communion really is and what it can accomplish taught the right way. Very well put together.

Truly eye-opening! The Lord's Supper is truly holy and set apart from the things of this world. Our Abba Father Wants Us Healed, Healthy, and Whole! And He has given us divine "medicine" straight from heaven through His Son Jesus' body, and we are freely forgiven forever of all our sins through His shed blood. Thank you Abba!
